ARAG CHANGELOG
===============

0.2 (Oct 19, 2007)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ADD: method execution based on request_method (GET, POST, etc). (Armen)
ADD: $CI (controller) object passed to all templates with "$this" name. (Armen)
ADD: Automatic validation implemented. (Armen)
ADD: arag_validation_errors smarty function plugin implemented to make life easier in validation hood. (Armen)
ADD: Form populatin implemented for smarty templates. (Armen)
ADD: Segments/GET validation implemented. (Armen)
ADD: Configuration model implemented. (Armen, Sasan)
ADD: Invalid request handler implemented. (Armen)
ADD: Subtabs of tabbedblock implemented. (Armen)
ADD: I18N implemented (based on gettext). (Armen)
ADD: extract_gettext.sh and format_gettext.sh scripts implemented. (Armen)
ADD: Sample module (Blog) implemented. (Armen)
ADD: create_schema.php script implemented, it can create a specifid database schema file(s) or all enabled modules schema files. (Armen)
ADD: Modules have their own config.php and routes.php files. (Armen)
ADD: Text helpers are implemented. (Sasan)
ADD: simple.tpl template for tabbedblock implemented. (Sasan)
ADD: Group actions are implemented for PList (Armen)
ADD: Icons are added for PList. (Armen)
ADD: arag_form smarty block plugin implemented. (Armen)
ADD: quote smarty fuction implemented. (Armen)
ADD: asterisk smarty function plugin implemented. (Armen)
ADD: arag_rte smarty plugin implemented (current RTE supports FCKeditor). (Sasan)
ADD: (Incomplete!) Initial version of user module imported. (Armen)
ADD: (Experimental, Incomplete!) Initial version of Authorization hook implemented. (Armen)

CHG: TabbedBlock changed due to subtabs implementation. *BC BREAK* (Armen)

FIX: Columns will shown in order that developer specified in code. (Armen)
FIX: Routing system didn't understand /<module_name> URIs but just /<module_name>/<class_name>/* (Armen)
FIX: Current method of routing system makes rsegments unusable, this problem fixed. (Armen)
FIX: CodeIgniter can't handle a directory name same as a controller name but it is handy tohave such ability. (Armen)
FIX: Do not throw an error when smarty wrapper is not exists for helper. (Armen)

0.1 (Oct 5, 2007)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

- Initial Release
